the stool pigeon ( simplified chinese : 线人 ; traditional chinese : 綫人 ; pinyin : xiàn rén ; jyutping : sin3 jan4 ) is a 2010 hong kong-chinese action thriller film directed by dante lam and starring nicholas tse , nick cheung and gwei lun-mei . the film is about police detective , don lee ( cheung ) , who uses informants to gain information about gangsters . lee begins to feel guilty when his informants are caught , but sends out a street racer named ghost ( tse ) as an informant to gain information about a gangster name barbarian ( lu yi ) . the film was released in china on august 24 and two days later in hong kong . the film performed well in the hong kong box office , though it has received mixed reviews .